FBIS3-6600 "dreas054_d_94031" FBIS-EAS-94-054 Document Type:Daily Report 19 Mar 1994 South Korea Kim Chong-il's Brother Becomes Envoy to Finland SK1903042294 Seoul CHOSON ILBO in Korean 19 Mar 94 p 2 SK1903042294 Seoul CHOSON ILBO Language: Korean Article Type:BFN [AFP, REUTER, YONHAP report from Helsinki] [Text] The Finnish Foreign Ministry officially announced that Kim Pyong-il, second son of North Korean President Kim Il-song, assumed office as North Korean Ambassador to Finland on 18 March.
